  "instructions": [
    "Heat the butter in the hot pot vessel over medium heat until melted.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for an additional 1 minute.",
    "Add the cod fish pieces and cook until browned on all sides, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the infuse oil, white wine, fish stock, lemon juice, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook until the fish is cooked through, about 10 minutes.",
    "Stir in the chopped parsley and serve hot.",
    "Serve the stew in bowls and garnish with additional parsley if desired."
